# Generated catalog artifacts
patterns/auto/

# Local-only MMSDM documentation capture (177 MB, analysis-only).
# See reference/NEMWEB-STRUCTURE.md §2.2 and reference/MMSDM-TABLE-LIFECYCLE.md
# for how to regenerate: every file lives under
# https://nemweb.com.au/Data_Archive/Wholesale_Electricity/MMSDM/{year}/MMSDM_{year}_{month}/MMSDM_Historical_Data_SQLLoader/DOCUMENTATION/
# INVENTORY.md is the recapture provenance manifest — kept in git as documentation.
reference/aemo-mmsdm-docs/*
!reference/aemo-mmsdm-docs/INVENTORY.md

# Local-only AEMO catalog capture (per-manifest + schema files, regeneratable).
# FETCH-MANIFEST.md is the capture provenance — kept in git as documentation.
reference/aemo-catalog/*
!reference/aemo-catalog/FETCH-MANIFEST.md

